Readme of Trader Sentiment Analysis
 
Overview
This project studies the relationship between Bitcoin market sentiment (Fear and Greed) and trader performance.
The goal is to understand how market mood affects trading activity, profit, loss, and risk-taking behaviour.
Objective
•	 Analyse trader profit and loss during Fear and Greed market conditions
•	Study trading behaviour like buy/sell decisions, leverage usage, and trade frequency
•	 Find useful insights that can help in making better trading strategies
Dataset 
 Bitcoin Market Sentiment Dataset
•	Columns: Date, Classification (Fear / Greed)
 Historical Trader Dataset
•	Columns: Account, Symbol, Execution Price, Trade Size, Side, Leverage, ClosedPnL, Time
Tools
•	  Python
•	  Pandas
•	  Matplotlib
•	  Google Colab
Conclusion
Market sentiment has a strong impact on trader behaviour and performance.
Understanding these patterns can help traders manage risk and improve trading decisions.
